Package cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.numbers

Class ScrFloat

java.lang.Object
cl.uchile.dcc.scrabble.types.numbers.ScrFloat
All Implemented Interfaces:
IOperations, SType
public class ScrFloat
extends java.lang.Object
implements IOperations
The ScrFloat class wraps a double in an object. A ScrBool object contains a single field whose type is double
